        <div class="text-content">
            <section>
                <h2>Your Safety Matters – Background-Checked Technicians for Reliable Appliance Repair</h2>
                <p>At <strong>[Your Company Name]</strong>, we prioritize your safety and peace of mind. That’s why all our <strong>appliance repair technicians are background-checked, vetted, and professionally trained</strong> to provide trustworthy, high-quality service in your home or business.</p>
