            <li><strong>Trust & Transparency</strong> – We believe in full transparency, which is why we share our commitment to hiring background-checked professionals you can trust.</li>
            <li><strong>Licensed, Insured, & Verified</strong> – Our appliance repair team is licensed, fully insured, and background-checked, ensuring accountability and professionalism in every service call.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>What Does Our Background Check Process Include?</h2>
        <p>At <strong>[Your Company Name]</strong>, we follow a strict hiring process to ensure trust and security for our customers. Our background screening includes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Criminal Background Checks</strong> – We verify that all technicians have clean records before hiring.</li>
            <li><strong>Employment Verification</strong> – We confirm previous experience, training, and skills.</li>
            <li><strong>Drug Testing & Screening</strong> – Ensuring our team is reliable and professional at all times.</li>
            <li><strong>Continuous Monitoring</strong> – We don’t just check once – we regularly update our screenings to maintain the highest safety standards.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>By choosing <strong>[Your Company Name]</strong>, you’re hiring a team of safe, responsible, and highly skilled appliance repair experts.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Appliance Repair Services You Can Trust</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Refrigerators & Freezers</strong> – Fixing leaks, temperature issues, and compressor problems.</li>
            <li><strong>Washers & Dryers</strong> – Addressing drainage problems, overheating, and mechanical failures.</li>
            <li><strong>Ovens & Stoves</strong> – Repairing burners, igniters, and heating inconsistencies.</li>
            <li><strong>Dishwashers</strong> – Resolving leaks, poor cleaning cycles, and clogged drain lines.</li>
            <li><strong>Microwaves & More</strong> – Troubleshooting power issues, faulty sensors, and broken doors.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Whether it’s a small repair or a complex fix, our background-checked technicians ensure quality workmanship, safety, and efficiency in every job.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Why Homeowners & Businesses Trust Us</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Same-Day & Emergency Repairs</strong> – Fast, reliable service when you need it most.</li>
            <li><strong>No Hidden Fees – Upfront Pricing</strong> – Transparent costs with no surprises.</li>
            <li><strong>All Major Brands & Models</strong> – We repair appliances from LG, Samsung, Whirlpool, GE, Maytag, Bosch, and more.</li>
            <li><strong>Satisfaction Guaranteed</strong> – We stand behind our repairs with a service warranty.</li>
